\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日都有賣廣告去到外國最好係當地買SIM卡<br />\n根本而家嘅policy係自相矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好係用email收otp<br />\n台灣獅子都可以咁做<br />\n係香港唔畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"#hk-no-it<br />\n<br />\n唔係因為email唔安全, 而係好多apps想借d意拎埋你電話contact list"},{"pid":"bbf012b6886e87b6d82251124f25c78e71551e85","tid":1037280,"uid":41308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"41f44e4c3e749c73919b71daa4166e99d3e1ec54","tid":1037280,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T01:12:24.000Z","msg":"睇到尾二嗰段覺得好怪，發言人唔出名？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:21:38.000Z","msg":"次次出事都有支那寶份 費時出名 影響跳槽"},{"pid":"32601da0cc90ee94c9114b1864d47b1ce47f70e6","tid":1037280,"uid":172468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"好彩我係用數碼通"},{"pid":"f6bf7ff7a566c9e65480a20e6b55f8fcec9bd77a","tid":1037280,"uid":769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:58:09.000Z","msg":"支那寶CLS"},{"pid":"191d2529c42c6fae6184944d527fbf7765437ab7","tid":1037280,"uid":173218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:16:25.000Z","msg":"想問仲用緊CSL既人係咩心態?收又唔係收得好"},{"pid":"15dda38a8703a559ff97807e7c5b2c13fd2135f6","tid":1037280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"支那寶好先進？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0dba307a36ca464a014270fdbacfa36927b6f3","tid":1037280,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15dda38a8703a559ff97807e7c5b2c13fd2135f6","tid":1037280,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"支那寶好先進？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T08:23:48.000Z","msg":"金管局對住支那野就唔使研究直接批，出咗事先算。<br />\n八達通加儲值上限都唔批，屌"},{"pid":"a0bb57053118ae921ace8f80ec11bc5f7277e072","tid":1037280,"uid":134618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T03:54:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}